data.description: Captivating single story home with close proximity to TWU and UNT. This house boasts a HUGE over-sized backyard with mature trees, covered patio, fire pit and finished outdoor shed with electric for gaming or entertainment. Inside, enjoy the tall vaulted ceilings, open living area and breakfast nook. This meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem promises both tranquility and accessibility, making it a haven for families seeking the perfect balance between natural beauty and modern amenities. Recent renovations include windows, roof and HVAC!
